column12:
'desc': [u'

Tomy Aqua Fun Paddling Pup Bath Toy Price: Rs.649

Tomy introduces this attractive bath toy for your little ones to play with. You can always make their bath time more fun-filled and entertaining by bringing home colorful bath toys. Tomy Aqua Fun Paddling Bath Toy is a unique and exciting toy that has a small cute puppy along with a ball. Kids who dislike bathing will love to take a dip in the water with this puppy in the tub. You can see their smiling faces by seeing this amazing puppy paddling in the tub and trying to chase the ball.

This Aqua Fun Paddling Bath Toy is sure to become your kid’s favourite bath toy and the vibrant colours of this toy will definitely catch your child’s attention. This Paddling Bath Toy is ideal for both boys and girls aged 12 months and above. Add this interesting and exciting bath toy to your child’s collection of toys and make their bath time more entertaining. They can easily hold this puppy and the ball and play with it. Let your little ones have fun playing with this Aqua Pup Bath Toy while taking a bath in the tub.

']
